  Config
  Toggle common config.toml settings for future turns.


  [ ] Update checks (current) (disabled)  Off for this internal app. Updates come from
                                          explicit internal releases. (disabled: Managed
                                          by iapp-codex.)
› [ ] Auth profile auto-switch            Switch to another configured profile after
                                          rate limits are exhausted.
  [*] Switch on 5h limit                  Allow auto-switching when the five-hour limit
                                          is exhausted.
  [*] Switch on weekly limit              Allow auto-switching when the weekly limit is
                                          exhausted.
  [*] Paste burst detection               Detect fast pasted input before inserting it
                                          into the composer.
  [ ] Hide reasoning summaries            Hide agent reasoning events from the
                                          transcript.
  [ ] Show raw reasoning                  Show raw reasoning content when the model
                                          emits it.
  [*] Environment context                 Include the environment_context block in
                                          model-visible context.

  Press space to toggle; esc to close
